resource.name: Incidents
resource.description: Use the charts, graphs, and maps below to look at our incident report data.  You can filter the data by any and all of the criteria below.  You can filter by offense type, year, beat, location, and zip code.

resource.name: JCPD Call Volume and Types of Calls
resource.description: The charts, graphs, and maps below show a breakdown of Johns Creek Police Department calls for service by type of call and also by date.  You can drill down into the data to see more details.

resource.name: Citation Data Analysis
resource.description: The charts, graphs, and maps below show a breakdown of Johns Creek Police Department citations that have been issued since 2010.  Click on this link (policeview.johnscreekga.gov/reports/Citations) to find out more about the Johns Creek Police Department traffic enforcement program.

resource.name: Johns Creek Accident Data Analysis
resource.description: Use the data navigators below to filter and visualize our accident data.  You can manipulate the data by date ranges, location, and causes.
